trans-unit.source: Enables users to change page-related print settings, including margins and paper orientation.
trans-unit.target: Gjør det mulig for brukere å endre siden-relaterte innstillinger, inkludert marger og arket retning.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan arves.

trans-unit.source: The PageSetupDialog dialog box modifies the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings> information for a given <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog.Document%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Dialogboksen PageSetupDialog endrer <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>og <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings>informasjon for en gitt <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog.Document%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog.Document%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>

trans-unit.source: The user can enable sections of the dialog box to manipulate printing and margins; paper orientation, size, and source; and to show Help and network buttons.
trans-unit.target: Brukeren kan aktivere delene av dialogboksen for å endre utskrift og marger; arket retning, størrelse og kilde; og til å vise Hjelp og knapper på nettverket.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog.MinMargins%2A> property defines the minimum margins a user can select.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog.MinMargins%2A>definerer minste margene en bruker kan velge.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog.MinMargins%2A>

trans-unit.source: When you create an instance of the PageSetupDialog class, the read/write properties are set to initial values.
trans-unit.target: Når du oppretter en forekomst av klassen PageSetupDialog, settes egenskapene lese-og skrivetilgang til opprinnelige verdier.

trans-unit.source: For a list of these values, see the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: En liste over disse verdiene i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: Because a PageSetupDialog needs page settings to display, you need to set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.Document%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.PrinterSettings%2A>, or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog.PageSettings%2A> property before calling <xref:System.Windows.Forms.CommonDialog.ShowDialog%2A>; otherwise, an exception will occur.
trans-unit.target: En PageSetupDialog krever sideinnstillinger skal vises, må du angi den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.Document%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.PrinterSettings%2A>, eller <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog.PageSettings%2A>egenskapen før du kaller <xref:System.Windows.Forms.CommonDialog.ShowDialog%2A>; ellers oppstår et unntak.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.CommonDialog.ShowDialog%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog.PageSettings%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.PrinterSettings%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.Document%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the margin settings, when displayed in millimeters, should be automatically converted to and from hundredths of an inch.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om for marger når vises i millimeter, automatisk skal konverteres til og fra hundredeler tomme.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings> class measures <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.Margins%2A?displayProperty=fullName> in hundredths of an inch, but the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog> allows users to set margins in inches or millimeters depending on the culture settings for the system running the application.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>klasse mål <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.Margins%2A?displayProperty=fullName>hundredeler tomme, men <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog>tillater at brukere marger er angitt i cm eller millimeter avhengig av kulturen innstillingene for systemet kjøring av programmet.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PageSetupDialog> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.Margins%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>

trans-unit.source: In the .NET Framework version 2.0, you should set this property to `true` if your application could be used in cultures that measure document margins in millimeters.
trans-unit.target: I .NET Framework, versjon 2.0, må du angi denne egenskapen til `true` Hvis programmet kan brukes i kulturer som måler dokumentet marger i millimeter.

trans-unit.source: If you are doing this conversion yourself, as was required in versions of the .NET Framework earlier than version 2.0, you should use the default value of `false`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du gjør dette konvertering selv, som er obligatorisk i versjoner av .NET Framework eldre enn versjon 2.0, bør du bruke standardverdien for `false`.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the margins should be automatically converted; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis margene automatisk skal konverteres; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
